Targets We expect all suppliers to commit to and follow our Supplier

Code of Conduct. This is also reflected in our DEGREE sustainability framework as a part of the Governance field of action.1

G Governance

Progress on DEGREE ambition #4: ESG-secured supply chain based on supplier commitment to our Supplier Code of Conduct

We expect our suppliers not only to contribute to the economic success of our company but also to ensure strict compliance with our sustainability require- ments, which are summarized in the Siemens Supplier Code of Conduct. The obligation of suppliers to observe our Code of Conduct is an essential founda- tion for fulfilling our governance ambitions bundled under “G” in our DEGREE sustainability framework.